parameters.description:
Only for repeating items. Identifies which occurrence to delete, as `yyyy-MM-dd`.
For repeating fixed-time items, use the date component of that occurrence's `startDateTime`;
For repeating auto-scheduled tasks, use the date component of that occurrence's `dueDateTime`.

Only for repeating tasks. Identifies which occurrence to edit, as `yyyy-MM-dd`.
For repeating fixed-time tasks, use the date component of that occurrence's `startDateTime`;
For repeating auto-scheduled tasks, use the date component of that occurrence's `dueDateTime`.

isAutoIgnored.description:
When a task can't be scheduled before its deadline: if `true`, the task is ignored; 
if `false`, it is scheduled after the deadline. Defaults to `true` for repeating tasks
and `false` for non-repeating tasks.
